fullplot: The year it took Dede Fortin to write and record "Dehors Novembre" is revisited in this doc. Swinging between crippling despair and fervent creativity, the past that haunted Fortin until his death lingers throughout, and serves as a poignant grace note for the creation of the band's last album.
